---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Link from "./ui/link.astro";
import Results250 from "assets/testimonial/results250m.png";
import Casestudy2 from "assets/casestudies/casestudy2.png";
import Resultsamazon from "assets/testimonial/resultsamazon.png";
import Picture from "astro/components/Picture.astro";
import Cleaningresults from "assets/testimonial/resultscleaning.png";
---

<h3 class="text-5xl text-center pt-16 font-bold lg:tracking-tight">
    Turning Goals into Results.
   </h3> 
   <p class="pb-12 pt-4 text-center ">
    We take pride in helping our clients- from small businesses to large corporations- achieve their goals. 
    </p>
   
    <div class="grid mb-6 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 align-items-center">
        <div class="bg-white mb-6 pt-4 pl-2 pr-2 pb-4 rounded-lg ml-2 mr-2 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl  border-2 border-black">
           
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold p-6 ">
                The Miracle Grand Opening of an Amazon Liquidation Business  | 1 Day, $1,000 Budget, 50k+ Sales.
            </h3>
            <p class="p-1 ml-3 font-bold rounded-3xl padding-left-2">
                Services Provided:
              </p>
           
            <p class="p-3 ml-3 font-bold bg-blue-200  rounded-3xl text-center inline-block align-center padding-left-2">
                Campaign
              </p>
              <p class="p-3 ml-3 font-bold bg-green-200  rounded-3xl text-center inline-block align-center padding-left-2">
                Content Creation
              </p>
            <Picture src={Resultsamazon} alt="Case Study" class="p-3 w-full h-100 object-cover rounded-lg " />

            <p class="text-sm p-6">
 A tight marketing budget and a small window of opportunity. We took this liquidation business to incredible feats using a clever marketing strategy that paid off big for our client., and then did it again..
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white mb-6 pt-4 pl-2 pr-2 pb-4 rounded-lg ml-2 mr-2 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl  border-2 border-black">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold p-6 ">
            Small Business, Big Reach. | 250 Million impressions in 3 months using Tiktok.
            </h3>
            <p class="p-1 ml-3 font-bold rounded-3xl padding-left-2">
                Services Provided:
              </p>
            <p class="p-3 ml-3 font-bold bg-blue-200  rounded-3xl text-center inline-block align-center padding-left-2">
                Campaign
              </p>
              <p class="p-3 ml-3 font-bold bg-green-200  rounded-3xl text-center inline-block align-center padding-left-2">
                Content Creation
              </p>
          
            <Picture src={Results250} alt="Case Study" class="p-3 w-full h-100 object-cover rounded-lg " />
            <p class="text-sm p-6">
                What started as a simple social media launch strategy for a small franchisee turned into a viral sensation. Leading to franchise record breaking numbers that left their corperate marketing office speechless..
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white mb-6 pt-4 pl-2 pr-2 pb-4 rounded-lg ml-2 mr-2 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl border-2 border-black">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold p-6 ">
            Squeaky Clean Marketing. | Tripling a Cleaning Service's Entire Business.
            </h3>
            <p class="p-1 ml-3 font-bold rounded-3xl padding-left-2">
                Services Provided:
              </p>
            <p class="p-3 ml-3 font-bold bg-blue-200  rounded-3xl text-center inline-block align-center padding-left-2">
                Campaign
              </p>
            <Picture src={Cleaningresults} alt="Case Study" class="p-3 w-full h-100 object-cover rounded-lg " />
            <p class="text-sm p-6">
                What started as a simple social media launch strategy for a small franchisee turned into a viral sensation. Leading to franchise record breaking numbers that left their corperate marketing office speechless..
            </p>
        </div>
        </div>
     
    </div>
    <div class="items-center align-center">
    <div class="flex justify-center">
        <button class="text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded">
            <Link href="/blog">View More</Link>
        </button>
    </div>
    </div>